Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:20.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是我.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:28.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 乔西.\N- 哈里, 我在这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Josie.\N- Harry, l'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,客房服务.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧, 门没锁.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in, it's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你把它放在桌子上就行了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just put it on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:56.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你睡的还不错吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l trust your sleep was untroubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在大北方这儿,\N我们的目标是让你住的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here at The Great Northern,\Nwe aim to make your stay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能舒适\N和愉快.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as comfortable\Nand as enjoyable as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道, 我们对客房服务\N的概念非常重视.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we take the concept\Nof room service very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得\N你爷爷?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember\Nyour grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个出色的人,\N我见过最聪明的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colorful man,\None of the wisest l ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他曾经说过?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what he once said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:22.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说如果你打算带上一个锤子\N的话, 最好也把钉子一起带上.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said if you're gonna bring\Na hammer, you better bring nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说下次\N你进来我房间时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What that means is the next time\Nyou come into my room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要继续进行下去,\N你最好随时准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and carry on,\Nyou'd better be ready to finish
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你进来这儿\N最开始想要做的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever it is\Nyou came here to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 也许我现在已经准备好了.\N- 然后做自己就好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Maybe l'm ready now.\N- Then be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在做我自己.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am being myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对正确.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我认错, 你是一个美丽,\N有才智的年轻女子.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l stand corrected, you're a beautiful,\Nintelligent young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:57.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你带有一种令人\N不可抗拒的魔力...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an undeniable\Nmagic about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...让我灵机一动.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that inspires a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在日暮中飞行之后2人晚餐如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight at sunset and dinner for two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 几时?\N- 什么几时, 在日暮中飞行?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- When?\N- What, the flight or the sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:11.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我还要去图书馆\N晚些还要和我爸见面.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l have to go to the library and\Nhave a meeting with my father later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就简单一句：去还是不去.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple yes or no would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:25.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那如果你要带锤子去的话,\N最好也带上钉子哦.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you bring a hammer,\Nyou better bring some nails too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:44.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 一句话也不说. 她要和\N南非领事馆谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a word. She wants to speak\Nto the South African consulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在双峰镇?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln Twin Peaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么埃卡想我死?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Eckhardt want me dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,性嫉妒.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:55.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了真好, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's good to have you back, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,晕船似的天旋地转\N花了我一天才回过神来.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taken me a day\Nor so to get my sea legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 老实说, 你看起来\N还真像刚下船的样子.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, it looks like\Nyou went down with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不回家\N好好休养一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go home\Nand recuperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 我只想喝点咖啡,\N或者再来点吃的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, all l need is some coffee,\Nmaybe a little food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是治愈宿醉的良方, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure-fire cure for a hangover, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿一杯几乎结冰的,\N未经过滤的番茄汁.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take a glass of nearly frozen,\Nunstrained tomato juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你扑通一声,把一对生蚝搭进去\N一口气喝光.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plop a couple of oysters in there,\Nyou drink it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后, 你再来一份劲量级的,\N我是说一份劲量级的牛羊杂碎,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you take a mound,\Nand l mean a mound, of sweetbreads,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伴点栗子\N和加拿大培根肉.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saute them with some chestnuts\Nand some Canadian bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最后, 再来个圆面包.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, biscuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大的, 整个闷浸到肉汁里.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big biscuits, smothered in gravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:28.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了现在, 这种吃法有个小秘诀,\N你一定加些凤尾鱼--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here's where it gets tricky,\Nyou're gonna need some anchovies--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就该那样做的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:43.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盆栽. 终极缩影.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bonsai. The ultimate miniature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小苏打水,\N终极助消化.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bicarbonate of soda,\Nthe ultimate digestive aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:53.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 一口气喝光就会好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, quaff in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个东东到底从什么鬼地方来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天上午送来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was delivered this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西送的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's from Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:19.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 云顿·厄尔\N来过我家了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, Windom Earle\Nwas at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:25.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔. 什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle. When?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:28.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天. 他把这个留给了唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday. He left this with Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他正接近, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's closing in, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:36.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,骑士对国王三主教.\N我们要该做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight to king bishop 3.\NWhat do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天要发布我们的下一步行动.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We publish our next move today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己可撑住了, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 戴尔·库珀探员.\N- 戈登·寇尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Agent Dale Cooper.\N- Gordon Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打断你们了，伙计们.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure sorry to interrupt you fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是, 库, 我给你带了\N云顿·厄尔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Coop, l'm bringing you\Nthe classified portion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:52.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,部分分类档案.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Windom Earle dossier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,Back from Bend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back from Bend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,刚从本德，俄勒冈州回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been on over to Bend, Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,整个本德\N到处都乱套了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whole lot of shaking\Ngoing on down in Bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登·寇尔也加入了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter Gordon Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这真叫人心烦, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so galling, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:13.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小戴尔正在不断拒绝\N公平游戏!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Dale is continually refusing\Nto play fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当时厄尔晕过去:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Earle went:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,医生发现\N他使用了强力安定药氟?啶醇.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the doctors discovered\Nhe was on haloperidol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和独臂人杰勒德\N以前用的药一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same drug the one-armed man,\NGerard, was on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:25.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?\N- 杰勒德用同样的药.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?\N- Gerard used the same drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:26.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你对了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们推测他是用\N这种药来装病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they figured he was using\Nthe drug to fake his illness
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所怀疑的, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just as you suspected, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明显是精神分裂病患的伎俩.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definite schizoid maneuvering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"蓝皮书计划?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Project Blue Book?''
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊, 戈登,\N他和这有什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God, Gordon,\Nwhat was he doing on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:47.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1965年，局里把厄尔\N借给空军部.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bureau loaned Earle out\Nto the Air Force in 1 965.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他那2年期间的报告\N都被涂黑删除了. 为了国家安全.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reports on his two-year hitch\Nare blacked out. National security.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:54.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔当时也在调查UFOs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earle was investigating UFOs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯少校, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Briggs, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登, 这里面的连接\N有古怪.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon, there are some\Ncurious linkages here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,连接这个词\N让我联想到了香肠.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word linkage\Nreminds me of sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别想太多什么连接了,\N不如想想小肉饼吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never cared much for the links,\Npreferred the patties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但早餐才是一个真正的好主意.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But breakfast is a real good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盆栽.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonsai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那些\N二战时期的老电影吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember those\Nold World War ll movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盆栽!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonsai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damnation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再次见到你真好, 医生.\N警长, 我们等一下和你们一起坐车.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you again, doc.\NSheriff, we'll be riding with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:27.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,巡警车就在外面等着.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cruiser's right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你留下来一会儿, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it one second there, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你赶快把自己那套\N尘封的黑西装解封吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better dust off\Nyour own black suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有云顿·厄尔\N在此兴风作浪,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Windom Earle\Nrolling around loose on the deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你重新归队.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need you back on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊, 戈登?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 我真高兴极了\N我正式通知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, it gives me great pleasure\Nto reinstate you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:44.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你复职\N回到联邦调查局.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into the Federal Bureau\Nof lnvestigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,全新发放的,\N更精准和高效.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-new issue,\Nmore accurate and efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,史密夫威信, 10毫米.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smith & Wesson, ten millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:55.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1076型号, 全不锈钢.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Model 1 076, all stainless steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一把漂亮的武器, 库,\N现在它都是你的了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a beautiful weapon, Coop,\Nand it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 戈登.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀, 我们一定要找到厄尔.\N我们会追捕,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper, we're gonna find Earle.\NWe will pursue,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:08.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 捉拿和监禁.\N- 捉拿和监禁.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- capture and incarcerate.\N- Capture and incarcerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们上路吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快跟上, 小鬼, 我请客.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, buster, l'm buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,紧随你尾后, 戈登.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your tail, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 里欧...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...选3张牌.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pick three cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,二,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,三.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:45.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:50.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉皇后, 好.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Shelly, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:59.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 看你能否找到国王.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, see if you can find the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小戴尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 我们还需要多一个皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need one more queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来瞧瞧看.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,红心皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The queen of hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰小姐.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 如果你赢了你会得到什么?\N你会得到一打玫瑰,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what do you get if you win?\NYou get a dozen roses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,得到你报读那所大学的\N奖学金,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a scholarship to the college\Nof your choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,得到你同辈们的赞美...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the accolades of your peers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 是, 我知道了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还会得到死亡.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个皇室般的处决仪式.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A royal execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而库珀...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cooper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...只能眼睁睁在那儿看着他们死去.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gets to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和你谈谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:09.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何, 先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was everything, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,简直好的超乎想像.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 欧蕊·荷恩在吗?\N- 她在后台. 我帮你去找她.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ls Audrey Horne here?\N- She's in the back. l'll get her for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨, 唐娜.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, Donna.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我能和你讲几分钟吗?\N- 当然可以.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can l talk to you for a minute?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这听起来可能有点儿奇怪.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might sound a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:43.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:48.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道有什么原因\N我妈会来探访你爸呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you know any reason\Nwhy my mom's visiting your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无头绪.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not offhand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:56.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恩, 是这样的, 昨天,\N他来我家见我妈.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, well, yesterday,\Nhe came by the house to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后今天,\N她就来这儿回访他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And today,\Nshe drove over here to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:01.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许她只是来帮他\N进行停止格斯伍计划而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's just helping him\Nwith the Stop Ghostwood campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 如果是的话，她会和我说的\N但她一个字也没提.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she would have said something\Nto me, and she hasn't said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她现在还在这儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls she here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一起在办公室里.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in his office together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 我不会接受它们的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l won't accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:20.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们是你的信.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们是写给你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were written to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要它们了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:27.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再把它们\N留在我家里了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't have them\Nin my house any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你都已经留着它们20年了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had them for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在才这样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我想问你的.\N为什么现在才这样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what l'm asking you.\NWhy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们只会把\N旧伤疤挖开.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll only succeed\Nin ripping apart old wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这儿我就受不了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't bear the thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:50.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳, 为什么你不相信我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eileen, why don't you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,口头说的不足以信.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words aren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:54.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要以行动来向你说明一切.\N难道你还没有听到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want my actions to speak for me.\NHaven't you been listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些年来我一直都是错的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have been wrong all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:17:00.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我尝试着去弥补它.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am trying to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:04.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但往往是\N做多错多.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, making up for things\Nonly makes it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 艾琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:13.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你本该是我一生人中\N拥有过最美好的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have been the best thing\Nthat ever happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 别这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自从那晚之后我就再也没抱过你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't held you since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我好想抱着你.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l wanna hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想回到过去.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 上帝, 如果你只是--\N- 求你了, 别这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- God, if you'd just--\N- Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你告诉她过吗?\N- 上帝啊, 没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have you told her?\N- God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:53.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从没有. 以后也不会.\N你必须答应我你也要做到.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never. l never will.\NAnd you must promise me the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对不可以再来找我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't come over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须离她远点.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你真的明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:18.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是在搞什么鬼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定要找出真相.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l'm gonna find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 有一个最好的解酒方法\N我每次碰到宿醉都管用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, the best cure l ever came\Nacross for a hangover
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是生肉, 吃很多很多生肉.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was raw meat, and plenty of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你打一个生蛋在上面.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You break an egg on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:41.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再加点腌渍凤尾鱼,\N土八哥辣椒仔和伍斯特郡劲辣油.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add in some salted anchovies,\NTabasco and Worcestershire sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想吃,\N我们可以帮你点一份.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you want,\Nwe can order up some for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在到我说了, 库,\N你知我现在想吃什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that l come to mention it, Coop,\Nyou know what l'm in the mood for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什么, 戈登?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一份5成熟的牛排,\N你可以在蒂芬妮珠宝店出售了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A steak so rare,\Nyou could sell it at Tiffany's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你可来对地方了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've come to the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:03.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,圣灵啊, 那是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy smokes, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个美人儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:20.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起那个雕塑,\N那个没手臂的小美人儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of reminds me of that statue,\Nthe babe without the arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 维纳斯·迪·麦咯.\N- 名字叫麦咯,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Venus de Milo.\N- The name was Milo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但那个是题外话了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩让你\N产生想讲点法语的愿望.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of girl to make you wish\Nyou spoke a little French.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:35.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下, 库, 我要去小柜台\N那边试试讲世界语了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Coop, while l try my hand\Nat a little counter Esperanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运, 戈登.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:46.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想能否麻烦你\N给我来一杯浓的原味黑咖啡.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was wondering if l might trouble you\Nfor a cup of strong, black coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:47.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在你煮咖啡的过程里,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:52.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你，会给你讲些非常\N好玩有趣的奇闻轶事.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,engage you with an anecdote\Nof no small amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我名字是戈登·寇尔,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name is Gordon Cole,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那卡座里\N就已经忍不住要注视你的美丽了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l couldn't help\Nbut notice you from the booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后...哇, 现在近距离看着你的美,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...well, seeing your beauty now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:06.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉彷彿装满了一胃大黄蜂\N心慌意乱，五脏六腑翻江倒海.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel as though my stomach is filled\Nwith a team of bumblebees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要说那么大声,\N我能听见.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to shout,\Nl can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了咖啡\N你还要别的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want anything\Nbesides coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能清楚听到你说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能听见你说话, 真的, 拜托了--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l can hear you, honest, please--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白, 强生小姐.\N你看见这些了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand, Miss Johnson.\NDo you see these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,20年来, 我一直要求\N别人一定要高声说话,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 20 years, l've been\Nasking people to please speak up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:33.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这实在太奇怪了,\N我竟能听见你声如洪钟.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some weird reason,\Nl can hear you clear as a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在说点别的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要来个馅饼送咖啡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want pie with your coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好家伙. 我能一清二楚的听见你说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Lord. l can hear you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:46.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可有点像奇迹降临了.\N一个超凡现象.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like some kind of miracle.\NA phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这算哪门子奇迹?\N- 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong with miracles?\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这樱桃馅饼才是一个奇迹.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cherry pie is a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:59.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你问这位拿圆木\N的女士大声点说话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please ask the lady\Nwith the log to speak up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是馅饼, 她刚刚\N樱桃馅饼的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pie, she was talking\Nabout the cherry pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:06.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我又听见你说话了. 我又听见你说话了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard you again. l heard you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要来点馅饼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来个巨大的, 有大量馅的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Massive, massive quantities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:15.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯水, 甜心,\N我浑身火烫啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a glass of water, sweetheart,\Nmy socks are on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,站在道奇跑车上的那只\N好像是山雀.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a chickadee\Non a Dodge Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:48.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不像, 道奇跑车上的\N倒像是一只百灵鸟.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it looks like a finch\Non a Dodge Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是, 道奇跑车上的是山雀.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, chickadee on a Dodge Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:56.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨.\N- 嗨. 来杯浓黑咖啡?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi.\N- Hi. Cup of deep black joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对解酒\N你有什么好方法介绍?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you recommend\Nfor a hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:06.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滴酒不沾和做祷告.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teetotaling and prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,回答的好.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来点咖啡吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll try some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天过得怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:18.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其实, 是怪异才对.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm weird, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷失方向了，都找不着北,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm disoriented,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道我现在在哪儿.\N我意思是, 我知道我在哪儿,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not sure where l am.\Nl mean, l know where l am,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:25.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但在这儿呆着让人感觉很古怪.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it feels odd being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:27.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:29.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说, 我一直在生活在\N社会之外，好长一段时间了,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, l've been out\Nof circulation so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:34.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些社交礼节\N我全都忘了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've completely forgotten\Nthe social niceties.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,比如, 你问我过得怎样阿,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, you ask me how l am,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会真的准确回答你\N我如何如何.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not really supposed\Nto say how l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:40.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想必会这样说,\N"我很好, 谢谢. 你呢"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm supposed to say,\N''l'm fine, thanks. How are you?''
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:43.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好, 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:49.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你肯定觉得我很奇怪.\N- 没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You must think l'm really strange.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:51.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过, 按照理应尊重的\N社会客套礼节,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with due respect\Nto the social niceties,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,既使你真的觉得我很奇怪,\N但你也不会对我说的, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you did think l was strange,\Nyou wouldn't tell me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事, 如果我认为你是个怪人,\N我会告诉你.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if l thought you were strange,\Nl'd tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而你不觉得?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:05.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好. 很高兴我们搞清楚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Glad we got that cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:07.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你要点什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:12.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要一个鸡肉夹馍\N和一份大杯装牛奶, 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like a chicken potpie\Nand a large glass of milk, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:15.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你很会点.\N所有主食都很具代表性.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good choice.\NAll the major food groups represented.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:19.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要火鸡三明治, 全麦的,\N生菜, 加一勺蛋黄酱,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turkey sandwich, whole wheat,\Nlettuce, dollop of mayonnaise,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:21.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我给你讲个笑话.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l've got a joke for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2只企鹅正走着\N准备翻过冰川.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two penguins were walking\Nacross an iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:27.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一只企鹅转过身来\N对第二只企鹅说:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One penguin turned\Nto the second penguin and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:29.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"你看起来像\N穿这一件晚礼服."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''You look like\Nyou're wearing a tuxedo.''
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:30.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到那个啦.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:35.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下, 我马上就回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, l'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没完全讲完呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wasn't quite finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:42.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱上她\N有多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long you been\Nin love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:45.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 谁说着和爱\N有关了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, who said anything\Nabout love?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 你刚刚还试着给她讲笑话呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, you just tried to tell her a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:52.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l did?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:58.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 那第二只企鹅\N怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did\Nthe second penguin say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 第一只企鹅\N对第二只企鹅说:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the first penguin said\Nto the second penguin:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:03.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"你看起来像\N穿这一件晚礼服."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''You look like\Nyou're wearing a tuxedo.''
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:07.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后第二只企鹅说,\N"我或许真的穿着晚礼服."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the second penguin said,\N''Maybe l am.''
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,终于自我圆场完毕了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.61,0:24:16.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想再来点馅饼吗?\N还是要整个馅饼?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some more pie?\NA whole pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:20.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 我会的, 强生小姐,\N还要一张纸和笔.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l would, Miss Johnson,\Nand a piece of paper and a pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:24.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我计划要为这个光芒四射的馅饼\N写一首叙事诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l plan on writing an epic poem\Nabout this gorgeous pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:26.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.41,0:24:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.68,0:24:35.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我见你去过猫头鹰山洞.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see that you've been to Owl Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.34,0:24:37.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:41.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 那个图案看起来就像一个\N面朝上的猫头鹰山洞.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.32,0:24:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that design looks like\Nthe one up at Owl Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.05,0:24:43.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看那个.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.33,0:24:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.05,0:24:46.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我把布里格斯少校的纹身\N和圆木姑姑的加在一起.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.33,0:24:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l combined Major Briggs' tattoo\Nwith the Log Lady's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:51.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这看起来的确\N像一个猫头鹰山洞.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.07,0:24:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks exactly\Nlike the one at Owl Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:55.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我得去看看这个猫头鹰山洞.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, l've got to see this Owl Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.36,0:25:16.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}亲爱的唐娜,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.63,0:25:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Donna,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.89,0:25:19.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你是对的, 我必须离开.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.13,0:25:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right, l had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.59,0:25:22.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但你上路了\N一切事就会不同了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything feels different\Nwhen you're on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.20,0:25:25.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这感觉好多了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.47,0:25:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt feels better.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.68,0:25:27.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}旧金山真的很酷.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.94,0:25:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,San Francisco's really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.91,0:25:30.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}下一站, 墨西哥.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.17,0:25:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next stop, Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:32.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我会带着无数故事回来的.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.64,0:25:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be back with a million stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.74,0:25:34.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我保证.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.01,0:25:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.57,0:25:37.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我爱你, 詹姆斯.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.85,0:25:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.11,0:25:48.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.36,0:25:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.64,0:25:50.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.90,0:25:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.38,0:25:52.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.63,0:25:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.86,0:25:54.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他正做其所需.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.13,0:25:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing what he needed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.21,0:25:57.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他会回来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.50,0:25:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.70,0:26:04.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸, 我能问你些事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.97,0:26:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, can l ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.49,0:26:05.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.74,0:26:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.84,0:26:07.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,妈怎么会认识\N本杰明·荷恩?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.11,0:26:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does Mom know\NBenjamin Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:12.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她不认识吧, 唐娜.\N不大清楚.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l doubt that she does, Donna.\NNot very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.54,0:26:14.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他昨天来过这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.82,0:26:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was over here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.29,0:26:16.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就像老朋友叙旧似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.55,0:26:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were talking like old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:18.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈和很多本地的\N慈善团体有工作关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.86,0:26:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother works a lot\Nwith the local charities.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.90,0:26:22.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定就连本也会\N捐助一次吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.19,0:26:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure even Ben contributes\Nonce in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:26.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她今早又开车去大北方\N见他去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She drove to The Great Northern\Nthis morning to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.74,0:26:29.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是谈\N募捐基金的事吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.00,0:26:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably something to do\Nwith a fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.49,0:26:30.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.77,0:26:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.27,0:26:34.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 确实是那样的,\N早餐时她和我说过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.54,0:26:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's exactly what it was,\Nshe told me at breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.10,0:26:37.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个关于『治愈我们的星球』计划的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.37,0:26:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those heal-the-planet things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:41.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 她没想我提过这事.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.85,0:26:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she didn't mention it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.94,0:26:44.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 事实就是这样,\N那时她告诉我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's exactly what it was,\Nthat's what she told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.65,0:26:49.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去开吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.92,0:26:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.27,0:26:56.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 我是来给海沃德太太\N送快递的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.53,0:26:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, l have a delivery\Nfor Mrs. Hayward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.81,0:27:06.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这花是送给妈的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.07,0:27:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they're for Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.68,0:27:08.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有贺卡.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.94,0:27:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No card.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.81,0:27:11.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去把它们养在水里.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.04,0:27:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll put them in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.08,0:27:37.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起, 对不起, 是我不好.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.34,0:27:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry, my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.43,0:27:40.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没听见你走过来.\N- 没事.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.70,0:27:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l didn't hear you.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.21,0:27:43.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有谁规定\N一个人的脑袋和一个人的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.51,0:27:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One should never allow\None's mind and one's foot
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.43,0:27:45.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要同步的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.71,0:27:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to wander at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.01,0:27:49.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾活·柏金斯.\N我再次向你道歉.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.28,0:27:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Perkins.\NOnce again, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.06,0:27:51.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊·荷恩.\N认识你真好, 柏金斯先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.32,0:27:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey Horne.\NNice to meet you, Mr. Perkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.71,0:27:55.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你在图书馆干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.99,0:27:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what brings you to the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.50,0:27:57.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在研究\N和平演变.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.75,0:27:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm doing research\Non civil disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.11,0:28:01.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你研究这个好. 现在就靠\N你们这些年轻人去抵抗了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.36,0:28:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you. lt is incumbent\Non the young to disobey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:03.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个教授吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.43,0:28:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.51,0:28:07.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 在我的领域里,\N教诗歌是我的专长.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.80,0:28:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l teach,\Npoetry is my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.69,0:28:11.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在开玩笑吧? 你知道吗, 有人\N给我寄了一首诗, 或许你读的懂.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.97,0:28:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding. You know, someone\Nsent me a poem, maybe you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.31,0:28:14.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 我可能会.\N现在, 我们来看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.60,0:28:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, perhaps l do.\NNow, let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.36,0:28:19.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你来读.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.61,0:28:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.85,0:28:22.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.11,0:28:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:25.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}看那山峰高耸入云,\N犹如波涛延绵不断{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the mountains kiss high heaven,\NAnd the waves clasp one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.07,0:28:29.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}没有一朵姐妹花会被宽恕\N如果它鄙视它的兄弟{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.32,0:28:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sister-flower would be forgiven\Nlf it disdain'd its brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.08,0:28:33.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}阳光紧扣着大地,\N月光则亲吻着大海{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.36,0:28:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the sunlight clasps the earth,\NAnd the moonbeams kiss the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.78,0:28:40.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}如果汝不吻我,\N这世间一切的甜蜜之事价值何在呢?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.06,0:28:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this sweet work worth,\Nlf thou kiss not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.92,0:28:42.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 你知道这首诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.20,0:28:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.71,0:28:45.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道. 是英国诗人雪莱的诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.97,0:28:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shelley.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.76,0:28:48.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.04,0:28:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.50,0:28:50.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.77,0:28:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazing at you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.81,0:28:53.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朗诵雪莱的诗,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,reciting the verse of Shelley,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.81,0:28:57.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来真的非常像一位皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.05,0:28:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you look very much like a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.91,0:29:01.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.19,0:29:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.96,0:29:05.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我要先走了.\N很高兴能遇见你.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.22,0:29:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess l better be going.\NNice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.88,0:29:08.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 或许某日我们会再相遇的.\N- 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.16,0:29:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Perhaps we'll meet again someday.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.78,0:29:29.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 想参加吗?\N- 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.05,0:29:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thinking of entering?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.31,0:29:31.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得就算没有这些\N穿这泳装和高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.58,0:29:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think the real world's strange enough\Nwithout getting on-stage
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.09,0:29:34.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上巡游的表演\N这个现实世界本身就已经够怪异了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.38,0:29:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and parading around\Nin a bathing suit and heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.66,0:29:37.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜修道院要是搞这样的东西\N地方肯定不够大.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.95,0:29:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess the convent's not too big\Non that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:38.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,猜的对.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.86,0:29:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.37,0:29:42.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 回到文明世界的\N感觉如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.62,0:29:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's it like being back\Nin civilization?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.03,0:29:45.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和我呆在修道院阁楼\N的确不一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.26,0:29:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not like they kept us\Nup in an attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.03,0:29:49.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 其实我们也读报纸,\N我们甚至还有有线电视.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.26,0:29:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, we had newspapers,\Nwe even had cable TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.17,0:29:53.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但每次我告诉别人我从哪来时，\N他们都表现的好像我刚从牢里放出来一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.44,0:29:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time l tell someone where l've\Nbeen, they act like l'm out on parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.61,0:29:56.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.91,0:29:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.88,0:30:00.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我觉得最怪是什么?\N又有男人在身边转悠了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.14,0:30:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what is weird?\NBeing around men again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.10,0:30:04.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 要是在修道院里的话\N你就没必要花时间去适应那个了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to spend time\Nin a convent to feel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.67,0:30:08.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你了解\N戴尔·库珀吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.95,0:30:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know\Nabout Dale Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.98,0:30:10.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们感兴趣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.25,0:30:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.59,0:30:11.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁这样说了?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.86,0:30:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.90,0:30:14.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔, 今天他看着你的时候\N光看他脸的表情就能判断了,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.16,0:30:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, judging by the look on his face\Nwhen he saw you today,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:16.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢说你的机会最大.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.99,0:30:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd say you have a major opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.56,0:30:19.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 你全搞错了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.86,0:30:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you have it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.13,0:30:21.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我对此还远远不感兴趣呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.43,0:30:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not even remotely interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.83,0:30:48.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.09,0:30:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.27,0:30:50.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.53,0:30:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.14,0:30:56.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想谢谢你昨天帮忙\N平息了鼬鼠骚乱.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.43,0:30:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna thank you for helping out\Nduring the weasel riot yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.28,0:30:59.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想对你说的话\N比对那个基巴要说的多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.54,0:31:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more than l can say\Nfor a certain Dick we both know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.42,0:31:03.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,维持秩序是我的份内事.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.67,0:31:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping the peace is part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.38,0:31:07.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你带着那齿轮\N准备去哪儿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.68,0:31:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going\Nwith all of that gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.47,0:31:09.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去洞穴勘探.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.78,0:31:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spelunking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.22,0:31:13.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,危险吗? 洞穴勘探?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.52,0:31:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it dangerous? Spelunking?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.36,0:31:18.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.53,0:31:20.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我点事行不?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.79,0:31:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.88,0:31:22.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.16,0:31:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.24,0:31:25.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你会很坚强,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.50,0:31:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know you'll be strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.72,0:31:28.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你会很勇敢,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l know you'll be brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.59,0:31:32.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要你答应我\N千万要小心.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.87,0:31:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l want you to promise me\Nthat you'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.78,0:31:37.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会小心的. 我向你保证.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.07,0:31:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be careful. You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.66,0:31:49.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢...亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.95,0:31:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.46,0:31:59.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 都搞好了, 哈里?\N- 皮特刚刚走出了我们的下一步.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.73,0:31:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All set, Harry?\N- Pete just called in our next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.25,0:32:03.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的卒向他的主教暴露了.\N- 要我打住吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.53,0:32:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We expose a pawn to his bishop.\N- Want me to hold off?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.22,0:32:04.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 皮特知道他在做什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.50,0:32:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Pete knows what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.78,0:32:06.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他吃了那只卒,\N他就会损失主教.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.07,0:32:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf he takes that pawn,\Nhe forfeits the bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.79,0:32:08.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 他就会前功尽弃了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.07,0:32:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, losing his initial advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.01,0:32:10.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.27,0:32:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.23,0:32:12.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像有人用一个铁道钉\N在我耳朵里猛捶猛穿一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.51,0:32:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like someone pounded\Na railroad spike through my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.93,0:32:15.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们到秘密洞穴里,\N去凉快凉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.18,0:32:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a descent into a cool,\Nsubterranean cave
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.45,0:32:18.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像医生吩咐的那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.71,0:32:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be just what the doctor ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.55,0:32:20.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,寇尔能\N爬上去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.78,0:32:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure Cole's up\Nfor the climb?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.33,0:32:21.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登不和我们去.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.59,0:32:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon's not coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.12,0:32:25.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉带他到海沃德医生那\N看他的听力去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.39,0:32:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly took him up to Doc Hayward's\Nto see about his hearing problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.47,0:32:28.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,老掉牙的音叉测试.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old tuning-fork test.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.03,0:32:47.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.28,0:32:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.47,0:32:50.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克·肯尼迪\N入主白宫时,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.71,0:32:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Jack Kennedy\Nentered the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.47,0:32:52.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他把他弟弟也接进去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.75,0:32:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he took his brother with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.52,0:32:55.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他相信波比\N会和他讲真话的,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.78,0:32:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he trusted Bobby\Nto tell him the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.87,0:32:58.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在不太顺境时.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.15,0:32:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when it wasn't pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.83,0:33:03.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当猪湾被炸毁时\N波比在那儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.09,0:33:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Bay of Pigs went up\Nin smoke, Bobby was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.19,0:33:07.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当俄国人把导弹扔进\N菲德尔·卡斯特罗的后院时,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.46,0:33:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Russians moved\Ntheir missiles into Fidel's backyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.63,0:33:11.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比在那儿帮助他的兄弟\N并肩作战.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.90,0:33:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby was there to help his brother\Nshoulder through.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.07,0:33:14.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指\N杰里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.34,0:33:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of how Jerry's done that\Nfor you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.90,0:33:20.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我寻找的正是\N这种毫无保留的真实.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.14,0:33:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the unvarnished truth\Nthat l am looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.48,0:33:24.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我相信你...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.78,0:33:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l believe that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.40,0:33:30.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...就是最佳人选.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are the best man for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.19,0:33:31.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.46,0:33:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.15,0:33:36.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.43,0:33:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.90,0:33:42.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我一直都\N是个不称职的爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.16,0:33:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that l haven't been\Na very good father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.30,0:33:48.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 真见鬼, 我这是在骗谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.57,0:33:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, heck, who am l kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.17,0:33:54.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我除了是一个低级庸俗的，贪婪的小人之外\N何时何事我有称职过的?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.44,0:33:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When have l ever been anything\Nbut a sleazy, rapacious heel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.40,0:33:58.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 爸爸,\N或许你在我小的时候称职过, 但--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.68,0:33:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Daddy,\Nmaybe when l was little, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.36,0:34:02.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是. 但我已经改过自新了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.62,0:34:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. But l've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.24,0:34:05.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我下定决心\N要做一个好人.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.49,0:34:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l am determined\Nto be a better person.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.90,0:34:12.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要成为那种\N你终有一日会尊重的父亲.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.16,0:34:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kind of father\Nthat you will respect someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.04,0:34:19.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我想到劳拉,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.33,0:34:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l think about Laura,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.14,0:34:23.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我想到我犯过的\N那些错误,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.41,0:34:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when l think about the mistakes\Nthat l've made,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.84,0:34:30.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到要为我们全家人\N构建一个幸福快乐的生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.11,0:34:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to build a life in happiness\Nfor our whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.98,0:34:33.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你, 我.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.25,0:34:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.64,0:34:37.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意帮助我去做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.92,0:34:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.04,0:34:40.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.32,0:34:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.57,0:34:44.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸, 我是你的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.83,0:34:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, l'm your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.09,0:34:47.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太让我感动了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.36,0:34:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensational.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.06,0:34:51.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 打点行装,\N赶去机场,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.33,0:34:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, pack a bag,\Nget out to the airport,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.58,0:34:53.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的航班一小时内起飞.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your plane leaves in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.63,0:34:55.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的航班?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.91,0:34:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.03,0:35:01.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 庄. 你来得刚好\N我正想找你呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:35:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, John. Just the man\Nthat l wanna see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.25,0:35:02.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 本. 你好, 欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.55,0:35:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ben. Hello, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.78,0:35:07.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸爸--\N- 欧蕊, 你最好快动身吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Daddy--\N- Audrey, you better get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.78,0:35:10.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1小时. 欧蕊今晚\N赶去西雅图.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.05,0:35:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hour. Audrey's on her way\Nto Seattle tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.66,0:35:13.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她会和环保主义者们\N一起参加早餐会议.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.92,0:35:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's having a breakfast confab\Nwith the environmentalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.66,0:35:17.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要把松鼬的事\N这个...推向全国.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.93,0:35:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going national\Nwith this...pine-weasel thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.98,0:35:19.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好极了, 那太好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.23,0:35:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.85,0:35:21.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸, 这么突如其来\N我不肯定我能马上走.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.10,0:35:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, l'm not sure l can leave\Non such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.20,0:35:25.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 这里是详情.\N时间, 地点, 等等.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.43,0:35:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here are the particulars.\NTime, place, so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.81,0:35:28.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 你要给我们带\N好消息回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.07,0:35:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, you bring us back\Ngood news.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.91,0:35:32.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好消息.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.18,0:35:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.61,0:35:38.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 我想我要走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess l better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.85,0:35:48.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 再见.\N- 再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.13,0:35:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bye.\N- Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.16,0:35:51.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心,  欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.43,0:35:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel safely, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.60,0:35:56.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,庄.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.90,0:35:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.92,0:36:05.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎样, 本?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.21,0:36:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.19,0:36:14.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉浑身都被\N灌满了仁慈和善良.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.45,0:36:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am filled to the brim\Nwith a feeling of goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.03,0:36:18.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像一颗圣诞树\N内心快活极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.29,0:36:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Christmas tree\Nall lit up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.99,0:36:25.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但每当夜里\N我看着镜子,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.29,0:36:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the end of the day\Nwhen l look in the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.70,0:36:32.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不面对一个事实\N就是我真的不知道怎么才算是好.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.96,0:36:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to face the fact\Nthat l really don't know how to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.49,0:36:34.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你正向着公平公正出发，相当好.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.77,0:36:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're off to a pretty fair start.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.76,0:36:37.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么做到的, 庄?\N有什么秘密吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.01,0:36:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do it, John?\NWhat's the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.50,0:36:41.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的认为\N我可以学着做一个好人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.78,0:36:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think\Nthat l could learn to be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.55,0:36:44.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没什么不可以啊.\N只要用心体会.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.81,0:36:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't see why not.\NJust keep your eye on your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.77,0:36:45.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且永远说真话.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.05,0:36:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And always tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.56,0:36:51.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 永远说真话.\N- 不过首先把最艰辛的真话讲出来.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.85,0:36:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Always tell the truth.\N- Tell the hardest truth first though.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.57,0:36:56.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 总是把最艰辛的真话先讲出来.\N噢, 我喜欢那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.86,0:36:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, always tell the hardest truth first.\NOh, l love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.27,0:36:57.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,庄, 那真是好极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.56,0:36:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John, that's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.14,0:37:02.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这说真话的事, 无疑是\N善良的最前线.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This truth business, it's clearly\Nat the forefront of goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.15,0:37:04.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.40,0:37:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.89,0:37:09.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我和你女儿相爱了.\N- 对, 这个真话够硬.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.14,0:37:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l'm falling in love with your daughter.\N- Yeah, that's a hard truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.77,0:37:12.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好例子.\N- 是真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.04,0:37:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good example.\N- lt is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.04,0:37:16.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的?\N- 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.35,0:37:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt is?\N- Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.57,0:37:22.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 庄.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.85,0:37:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.88,0:37:25.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 庄.\N- 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.15,0:37:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- John.\N- Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.62,0:37:30.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们身处的世界多美好啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.89,0:37:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful world we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.35,0:37:45.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小心点, 安迪.\N- 抓紧了, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.61,0:37:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, Andy.\N- Get a good grip, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.18,0:37:46.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看到了.\N- 就是那, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.44,0:37:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do it.\N- That's it, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.48,0:37:49.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看来很好.\N- 手把手.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.74,0:37:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Looking good.\N- Hand over hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.92,0:37:51.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快到了. 放松点.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.21,0:37:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.53,0:37:54.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不, 别, 别. 别往下看. 别.\N- 撑住了, 安迪. 别往下看.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.82,0:37:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, no, no. Don't look down. No.\N- Hang on, Andy. Don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.84,0:37:56.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 坚持住.\N- 别往下看!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.09,0:37:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hang on.\N- Don't look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.64,0:38:01.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 安迪.\N- 你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.89,0:38:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Andy.\N- You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.03,0:38:03.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.26,0:38:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:11.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.57,0:38:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lncredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.31,0:38:14.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们小的时候\N常常在这儿玩.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.60,0:38:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to play here\Nwhen l was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.97,0:38:17.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,假装那是恶灵\N在闹鬼.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.24,0:38:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that it was haunted\Nby fierce ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.93,0:38:19.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是酒鬼留下的.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.21,0:38:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beer drinkers, by the look of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.06,0:38:22.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个符号在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.35,0:38:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.80,0:38:24.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这边.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.08,0:38:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.13,0:38:37.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.39,0:38:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.45,0:38:46.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.74,0:38:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.51,0:38:57.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2个符号合并成\N一个完整的大符号.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.78,0:38:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two symbols combined\Ninto a larger whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.73,0:38:59.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但那意味着什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.02,0:38:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.95,0:39:01.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.25,0:39:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.52,0:39:02.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可问倒我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.74,0:39:05.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纹身代表问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.02,0:39:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tattoos are the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.05,0:39:07.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那这个一定就是答案了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.32,0:39:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.68,0:39:47.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,卡住了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.93,0:39:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:50.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的镐子, 卡住了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.37,0:39:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pick, it's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.57,0:39:57.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的天哪.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.84,0:39:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.30,0:40:18.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,圣烟啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.59,0:40:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.87,0:40:24.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看那个.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.17,0:40:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.50,0:40:32.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我都干了什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have l done?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.33,0:40:39.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们, 我们的生活\N大多是要靠巧合和运气.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.58,0:40:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fellas, coincidence and fate\Nfigure largely in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.74,0:40:52.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出现的是一个岩石雕塑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.03,0:40:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt appears to be a petroglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.71,0:40:57.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我不知道\N这将会把我们领向何方.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.00,0:40:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, l have no idea\Nwhere this will lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.63,0:41:04.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我明显感觉到\N它将是一个既惊奇又怪异的地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.90,0:41:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l have a definite feeling it will be\Na place both wonderful and strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.00,0:41:41.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好.\N我能帮你点什么, 小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.28,0:41:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.\NCan l help you, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.35,0:41:45.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 我想来点喝的,\N但我不确定想喝什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.65,0:41:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l would like something to drink,\Nbut l'm not exactly sure what.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.23,0:41:47.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,淑女们似乎都喜欢喝朗姆酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.48,0:41:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies seem to like the rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.19,0:41:50.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朗姆酒. 就来杯朗姆酒吧\N谢谢 .
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.45,0:41:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rum. l would like to have\Na rum, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.07,0:41:53.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 加...?\N- 汤力水?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.32,0:41:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- With...?\N- Tonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.68,0:42:01.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 星期四, 晚上9:05.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.93,0:42:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, Thursday, 9:05 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.86,0:42:04.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚从一个叫猫头鹰山洞\N的地方回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.13,0:42:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've just returned from a place\Ncalled Owl Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.87,0:42:07.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至于我是怎么去到那里\N是一个相当复杂的故事.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.17,0:42:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How l got there\Nis a rather complicated story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.31,0:42:10.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情都起源于一对纹身...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.57,0:42:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt all began with a pair of tattoos...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.11,0:42:21.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一杯我请.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.35,0:42:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First one's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.38,0:42:22.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.62,0:42:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.94,0:42:24.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好, 安妮.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.19,0:42:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello, Annie.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.69,0:42:27.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我给你买什么喝的--?\N- 不, 不用了. 我有汤力朗姆酒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.99,0:42:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can l get you something--?\N- No, no. l have a rum and tonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.60,0:42:28.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.89,0:42:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.95,0:42:30.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个姐姐\N以前常把朗姆酒加到茶里,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.23,0:42:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the sisters\Nused to put rum in her tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.96,0:42:33.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时听来像是天方夜谭, 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.23,0:42:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l thought it sounded exotic, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.35,0:42:34.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切对你来说都是新的, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.63,0:42:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all new to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.01,0:42:40.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得惊奇不断, 好眩.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.30,0:42:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel constantly amazed, stunned.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.54,0:42:42.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐和人,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.81,0:42:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Music and people,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.93,0:42:44.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们讲话和笑的方式,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.17,0:42:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way they talk and laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.11,0:42:47.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而他们中有些人\N很明显是爱人.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.38,0:42:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the way some of them\Nare so clearly in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.55,0:42:49.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说就像是外语一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.81,0:42:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's like a foreign language to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.55,0:42:52.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我意识到言语不足以表达\N我懂的有多么少啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.85,0:42:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know just enough of the words\Nto realize how little l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.47,0:42:55.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗳, 我喜欢透过你眼睛\N去看世界.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.75,0:42:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, l would love to see the world\Nthrough your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.61,0:42:57.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.89,0:42:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.87,0:43:01.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 如果我有机会\N我可能会去做些不同的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.16,0:43:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's some things\Nl might do different if l had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.75,0:43:03.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.03,0:43:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.77,0:43:21.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧, 世事就是如此,\N我以前失败过，而...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.04,0:43:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the thing is,\Nl failed before and...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.40,0:43:28.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕它会再次发生.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.65,0:43:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm just afraid it might happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.01,0:43:31.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说说它吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.29,0:43:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.97,0:43:34.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不想说.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.22,0:43:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.41,0:43:37.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我能帮助你.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.66,0:43:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe l can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:40.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.66,0:43:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.03,0:43:42.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.27,0:43:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.95,0:43:46.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很倔强的. 又极其任性.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.24,0:43:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm stubborn. Extremely willful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.00,0:43:48.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能应付得来.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.27,0:43:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.61,0:43:51.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人觉得我是个怪人.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.91,0:43:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people think l'm strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.70,0:43:53.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那是什么感觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.98,0:43:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.66,0:43:58.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能向你保证\N我总是理性的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.91,0:43:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l couldn't promise you\Nthat l would always make sense
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.15,0:44:01.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或者去做些\N你期待我去做的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.42,0:44:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or do things\Nthat you would expect me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.46,0:44:03.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮, 我不予任何冀望.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.72,0:44:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie, l don't expect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.64,0:44:08.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧，我接受你仁慈\N和慷慨厚意.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.89,0:44:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l accept your kind\Nand generous offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.95,0:44:13.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好. 我很高兴.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.23,0:44:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. l'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.56,0:44:39.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的, 我的, 我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.85,0:44:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.43,0:44:42.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看我们在这...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.73,0:44:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.57,0:44:44.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...找到了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.83,0:44:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.40,0:44:48.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是它吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.66,0:44:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.63,0:44:53.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.87,0:44:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.68,0:44:57.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,倒转的符号.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.94,0:44:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The symbol inverted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.17,0:45:05.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.45,0:45:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
